{"tid":610411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咖啡致癌？】加州法官裁定 星巴克等咖啡公司要貼致癌警告標籤","createTime":"2018-03-30T02:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T02:52:19.000Z","uid":47272,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f984f76a773feccb5059666d83e8d0e368507ca7","tid":610411,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180330&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58013001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180330%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58013001&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d674ef31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180330%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58013001&h=0ed5e3a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180330&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58013001</a><br />\n美國洛杉磯法院裁定，由於咖啡在烘焙過程中產生的一種化學物質有致癌風險，星巴克（Starbucks）等咖啡公司必須在於當地銷售的產品上貼上警告標籤。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯最高法院法官伯利(Elihu Berle)在裁決中指出，星巴克及其他咖啡公司未能證明該種化學物質的致癌風險是極微。<br />\n<br />\n一個非牟利組織引用加州法例控告星巴克及其他約90間雜貨店及零售商，指咖啡在烘焙過程中會產生致癌化學物質丙烯酰胺(acrylamide)，不過咖啡公司未有依照法例在產品上加添致癌警告。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判詞中指出，被告人未能滿足舉證責任－－就是飲用咖啡對人類健康有益。<br />\n<br />\n咖啡公司則辯稱，咖啡內的丙烯酰胺含量，處於無害水平，因此應獲法例豁免。星巴克和此案其他原告得在4月10日前提出異議。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"5be82ae2ba6e32f851caa46c77ce35875af0cc45","tid":610411,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f984f76a773feccb5059666d83e8d0e368507ca7","tid":610411,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180330&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58013001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180330%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58013001&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d674ef31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180330%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58013001&h=0ed5e3a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180330&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58013001</a><br />\n美國洛杉磯法院裁定，由於咖啡在烘焙過程中產生的一種化學物質有致癌風險，星巴克（Starbucks）等咖啡公司必須在於當地銷售的產品上貼上警告標籤。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯最高法院法官伯利(Elihu Berle)在裁決中指出，星巴克及其他咖啡公司未能證明該種化學物質的致癌風險是極微。<br />\n<br />\n一個非牟利組織引用加州法例控告星巴克及其他約90間雜貨店及零售商，指咖啡在烘焙過程中會產生致癌化學物質丙烯酰胺(acrylamide)，不過咖啡公司未有依照法例在產品上加添致癌警告。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判詞中指出，被告人未能滿足舉證責任－－就是飲用咖啡對人類健康有益。<br />\n<br />\n咖啡公司則辯稱，咖啡內的丙烯酰胺含量，處於無害水平，因此應獲法例豁免。星巴克和此案其他原告得在4月10日前提出異議。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"要自己證明自己無罪?<br />\n咁似某國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5a1ff56915db2d293c4c4e2f71627512a9d78b","tid":610411,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc31b0552d5cd22f320d74efd31c328407037713","tid":610411,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁薯片薯條呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b6f29537aa9f70b22ef1903cb8fd74de0ca14e","tid":610411,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc31b0552d5cd22f320d74efd31c328407037713","tid":610411,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁薯片薯條呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.calbizlit.com/.a/6a00d83451e4e569e201310fb153de970c-pi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calbizlit.com%2F.a%2F6a00d83451e4e569e201310fb153de970c-pi&h=dcc960f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7d/Disneyland_Prop_65_Warning_crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F